text:
Worst behavior and attitude!!!

Ordered steak and aglio olio to dine in.  Instead, they packed it up so as to charge extra for the packaging.  Refused to acknowledge mistake and even rolled eyes when confronted.

Steak was rubber.  Aglio Olio overcooked and bland.  Badly frozen and salted fried wings.  The only western store here though, if you were desperate enough

Specky young plump lady taking orders with bad attitude and rude. Talked in short and unhappy tone. My first and last time ordering from this stall. Cannot understand why so young and already got this kind of bad attitude. Horrible.
